WEBVTT

00:01.274 --> 00:03.091
<i>Previously on</i> Mike & Molly...

00:03.092 --> 00:04.117
You guys did very well.

00:04.118 --> 00:06.747
I think you're perfect
candidates for adoption.

00:06.748 --> 00:07.747
Oh, that's great.

00:07.748 --> 00:10.117
Thank you so much.

00:10.118 --> 00:13.077
So, the next thing for us to do
is schedule a home visit.

00:13.078 --> 00:14.118
Whose home?

00:16.288 --> 00:18.457
Yeah, we are totally committed

00:18.458 --> 00:20.697
to creating a healthy
and safe environment

00:20.698 --> 00:21.957
- for this child.
- Yeah.

00:21.958 --> 00:24.457
I promise you, we will
take good care of it.

00:29.408 --> 00:31.537
I appreciate you being
so thorough and open.

00:31.538 --> 00:33.907
Most couples hoping to adopt
aren't as forthcoming.

00:33.908 --> 00:36.117
So, about your living situation.

00:36.118 --> 00:38.158
- We live alone.
- Just the two of us.

00:42.868 --> 00:44.907
Why do we have to take
new holiday photos

00:44.908 --> 00:46.577
for the adoption agency?

00:46.578 --> 00:50.037
I mean, I look fantastic
in these old ones.

00:50.038 --> 00:51.657
Because we have to show
expectant mothers that,

00:51.658 --> 00:53.747
if they pick us,
that their child will be raised

00:53.748 --> 00:55.457
in a safe
and wholesome environment.

00:55.458 --> 00:57.457
What's not wholesome here?

00:57.458 --> 00:59.115
Wine glass.

00:59.868 --> 01:00.908
Shot glass.

01:02.118 --> 01:03.118
Beer bong.

01:04.578 --> 01:06.395
Bong bong.

01:06.655 --> 01:09.157
Okay, all right,
let's make some memories, people.

01:09.158 --> 01:11.497
Victoria, hold the branch up.
Mike, grab an ornament.

01:11.498 --> 01:12.617
Mom.

01:12.618 --> 01:14.578
Get a shot of us decorating
the Christmas tree.

01:19.823 --> 01:20.862
Got it!

01:20.863 --> 01:22.653
Okay, next.
Lose the sweater!

01:23.943 --> 01:25.782
Okay, we got to celebrate
two birthdays,

01:25.783 --> 01:26.992
we got to carve some pumpkins,

01:26.993 --> 01:29.072
we got to pose for
that Fourth of July picture

01:29.073 --> 01:32.032
in front of the neighbor's pool
before they get home.

01:32.033 --> 01:35.903
Are we doing Halloween now or do
I have time to run to Costco?

01:38.823 --> 01:42.112
