01:42.113 --> 01:44.992
♪ La, la-ba-dee-da ♪

01:44.993 --> 01:47.942
♪ For the first time
in my life ♪

01:47.943 --> 01:49.612
♪ I see love ♪

01:49.613 --> 01:51.742
♪ <i>I see love</i> ♪

01:51.743 --> 01:54.652
♪ For the first time
in my life ♪

01:54.653 --> 01:56.282
♪ I see love ♪

